# Livewire Upgrade

## When to use

- Upgrading Livewire v2 to v3
- Upgrading Livewire v3 to v4
- Fixing `wire:model` breaking changes (deferred by default in v3)
- Migrating Livewire events (`emit` to `dispatch`)
- Handling Alpine.js integration changes after Livewire upgrade

## Keywords

`livewire upgrade`, `livewire v2 to v3`, `livewire v3 to v4`, `wire:model`, `livewire dispatch`, `livewire breaking changes`, `livewire volt`
